snippet.title: MONZO VR | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Enter your virtual Zen workshop and bring your dreams to reality in Monzo VR. With over 30
digital modelling kits, you will soon lose yourself in the art of creation. Monzo VR will be soon available for you to play it on OCULUS RIFT and GEAR VR.

Visit and subscribe at our WEB page to get chance to participate in BETA testing. http://bit.ly/MonzoVRyt



You may also find more information on our social sites:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/monzo
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MADFINGERGames
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/MadFingerGames
